RIE is a Brussels based AISBL and as such had four founding members. These are:&#xd;
1. V. Giscard d'Estaing, former President of France, President of Re-Imagine Europa;&#xd;
2. E. Widegren, Chief Executive of RIE&#xd;
3. L. Aguirre, former Editor-in-Chief of El Pais.com and Chief Digital Officer of RIE &#xd;
4. O. Giscard d'Estaing, Strategic Adviser to RIE
